room_title: Escape room "The Shadow Gallery" by The Clue Room in Denver
room_description: The year is 2020, a woman only known as ‘The Traveler’ – named for her habit of stealing and collecting rare artifacts from around the globe, is set on finishing the job her mentor began five priors by attacking the city of London. As New Scotland Yard Detectives, you must infiltrate her lair – The Shadow Gallery – and stop her before she can terrorize the whole world!
